<h1>PASTA</h1>
<center><img src="pasta.jpg" alt="Pasta" width="400" height="400"></center>
<p>a dish originally from Italy consisting of dough made from durum wheat and water, extruded or stamped into various shapes and typically cooked in boiling water.</p>
